<h1>Welcome to MyQuote</h1>

<div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <p>
        Discover a world of inspiration and wisdom with <strong>MyQuote</strong>, your personal quote collection and sharing platform. Here, you can explore famous quotes, save your favorites, and even contribute your own pearls of wisdom.
      </p>

      <div class="jumbotron mt-4 p-4 bg-light">
        <h2>Why MyQuote?</h2>
        <p>
          We believe that words have the power to transform lives. Whether you're looking for motivation, insight, or a moment of reflection, MyQuote offers a unique way to connect with the thoughts and ideas of some of history's greatest minds.
        </p>
        <p>
          <%= link_to 'Get Started', new_user_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %> and begin your journey to discovering and sharing the wisdom that moves you!
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Popular Categories</h2>
      <p>Explore quotes by topic:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to 'Motivation', category_path(Category.find_by(name: 'Motivation')) %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Wisdom', category_path(Category.find_by(name: 'Wisdom')) %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Life', category_path(Category.find_by(name: 'Life')) %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Philosophy', category_path(Category.find_by(name: 'Philosophy')) %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'Happiness', category_path(Category.find_by(name: 'Happiness')) %></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Discover thousands of quotes by famous philosophers, authors, and thinkers.</li>
        <li>Create a personalized account to save and manage your favorite quotes.</li>
        <li>Contribute your own quotes and share your wisdom with the world.</li>
        <li>Browse quotes by category, philosopher, or theme.</li>
        <li>Enjoy a clean and user-friendly interface, designed to make finding inspiration easy.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Join Us Today</h2>
      <p>
        <%= link_to 'Sign up now', new_user_path %> to start creating your own collection of inspiring quotes and join a community of like-minded individuals.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
